.::[ ArchTrack AUR slurpie v0.2 ]::.
- copyleft
- fnord0@riseup.net

USAGE: ./atslurpie.pl [-n] <search string> [-f <filename> {-s}]
                                                                                                                                                                        
COMMAND LINE ARGUMENTS
        -n              => search the AUR tool 'name' field only
        <search string> => your AUR search string
        -f <filename>   => search the AUR using a file, with 1 search per line
        -s              => sort the input file searches NUMBERIC-alphabetically
        --help          => displays this help
        --version       => displays version information

                EXAMPLEs:  atslurpie.pl gdb
                           atslurpie.pl -nsf /tmp/listofsearches.txt                                                                                                    
                           atslurpie.pl -n metasploit 
